.PP
The output from this script includes:
.TP 3n
\(bu
Minimum values for the
DataMemory,
IndexMemory,
MaxNoOfTables,
MaxNoOfAttributes,
MaxNoOfOrderedIndexes,
MaxNoOfUniqueHashIndexes, and
MaxNoOfTriggers
